  "instructions": [
    "In a small bowl, mix together shio-koji and 1 tablespoon of water to make a paste.",
    "In a large cazuela, heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the brie cheese and cook until melted and bubbly, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the lemon juice and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and top with parsley.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
